resources NI(19),FI(14.5)
notes
PIs of the SP: Keisuke Hosokawa (UEC) and Ilkka Virtanen (Oulu Univ.)

We conduct simultaneous observations of pulsating aurora with 
the EISCAT UHF/VHF system and KAIRA, to investigate polarization 
electric field associated with pulsating aurora.
We prefer good weather condition for optical observations.

